# Environment variables

# This portfolio app does not require environment variables to build or run.
# Network I/O uses MockChatTransport (no API keys).
#
# If you add a production ChatTransport (WebSocket, REST, Firebase), document
# required variables here and load them via Xcode build settings or xcconfig
# files that are excluded from git (see .gitignore).
#
# Example (do not commit real values):
# CHAT_API_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com
# CHAT_WS_URL=wss://api.example.com/ws
